title: Need some Expertise: Odd[?] printer's mark and "wet sheet transfer"?--
author: dougscats

posts.post_title: Need some Expertise: Odd[?] printer's mark and "wet sheet transfer"?--
posts.post_content:
A little help, please: 

Is this printer's mark in the right-hand border [as distinguished from the other mark in the bottom border] unusual?  

Also, it looks to me like the back has some ink color, presumably absorbed from the card that laid beneath.  I don't want to glorify these smudges, but would they be called wet sheet transfer? 

I include it in B/S/T as, with no great expectations, I'll field offers on the card.  

Thanks for your input.
